    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Speed and comfort",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.17,
      "endTime": 8.92
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Which type of transport does the writer prefer, do you think?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 8.93,
      "endTime": 15.04,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "People travelling long distances frequently have to decide whether they would prefer to go by land, sea, or air.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.05,
      "endTime": 23.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Air",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "空格"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Hardly anyone can positively enjoy sitting in a train for more than a few hours.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.94,
      "endTime": 30.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Train compartments soon get cramped and stuffy.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 30.98,
      "endTime": 34.85
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It is almost impossible to take your mind off the journey.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34.86,
      "endTime": 39.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Your",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你的，你们的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Reading is only a partial solution, for the monotonous rhythm of the wheels clicking on the rails soon lull you to sleep.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "endTime": 49.09,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "During the day, sleep comes in snatches.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 49.1,
      "endTime": 52.89
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "At night, when you really wish to go to sleep, you rarely manage to do so.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.9,
      "endTime": 58.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "If you are lucky enough to get a sleeper,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 58.6,
      "endTime": 61.42,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "you spend half the night staring at the small blue light in the ceiling, or fumbling to find your ticket for inspection.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.43,
      "endTime": 70.9,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Blue",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "蓝色的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Your",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你的，你们的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Ticket",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "票"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Inevitably you arrive at your destination almost exhausted.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.91,
      "endTime": 77.12,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Your",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你的，你们的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Long car journeys are even less pleasant, for it is quite impossible even to read.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.13,
      "endTime": 83.67,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Car",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "轿车"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "On motorways you can, at least, travel fairly safely at high speeds,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 83.68,
      "endTime": 89.3,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "but more often than not, the greater part of the journey is spent on roads with few service stations and too much traffic.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.31,
      "endTime": 98.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Too",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "也"
          },
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "By comparison, ferry trips or cruises offer a great variety of civilized comforts.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 98.94,
      "endTime": 106.93
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "You can stretch your legs on the spacious decks, play games,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 106.94,
      "endTime": 110.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "Your",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你的，你们的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "meet interesting people and enjoy good food--always assuming, of course, that the sea is calm.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 111,
      "endTime": 120.52,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Meet",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "遇见，结识"
          },
