            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If it is not, and you are likely to get seasick, no form of transport could be worse.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.53,
      "endTime": 128.14,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Even if you travel in ideal weather, sea journeys take a long time.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 128.15,
      "endTime": 133.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Relatively few people are prepared to sacrifice holiday time for the pleasure of travelling by sea.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 133.69,
      "endTime": 141.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Aeroplanes have the reputation of being dangerous and even hardened travellers are intimidated by them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 141.98,
      "endTime": 149.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They also have the disadvantage of being an expensive form of transport.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 149.86,
      "endTime": 155.67
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But nothing can match them for speed and comfort.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 155.68,
      "endTime": 160.06,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Travelling at a height of 30, 000 feet, far above the clouds, and at over 500 miles an hour is an exhilarating experience.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 160.07,
      "endTime": 171.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "You do not have to devise ways of taking your mind off the journey, for an aeroplane gets you to your destination rapidly.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 171.17,
      "endTime": 179.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Your",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你的，你们的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "For a few hours, you settle back in a deep armchair to enjoy the flight.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 179.72,
      "endTime": 186.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The real escapist can watch a film and sip champagne on some services.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 186.26,
      "endTime": 192.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Watch",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "手表"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But even when such refinements are not available, there is plenty to keep you occupied.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 192.79,
      "endTime": 198.56,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "An aeroplane offers you an unusual and breathtaking view of the world.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 198.57,
      "endTime": 204.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "You soar effortlessly over high mountains and deep valleys.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 204.61,
      "endTime": 209.83,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "You really see the shape of the land.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 209.84,
      "endTime": 212.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "If the landscape is hidden from view,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 212.94,
      "endTime": 215.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "you can enjoy the extraordinary sight of unbroken cloud plains that stretch out for miles before you, while the sun shines brilliantly in a clear sky.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 215.59,
      "endTime": 228.88,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The journey is so smooth that there is nothing to prevent you from reading or sleeping.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 228.89,
      "endTime": 235.61,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
